lexa.core.data

Class BaseDataSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • lexa.core.data.BaseDataSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<DataItem>, DataSet
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HashDataSet, SimpleDataSet

    public abstract class BaseDataSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataSet
    Provide the base methods for a data set.

    This provides the getters for the specific types supported. It does not implement the basic get method

    Author:
    william
